    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor just gave me a generic script and didn't really explain why i need 10 days if the skin already looks normal. honestly it feels like overkill. if the infection is gone, isn't the medicine just unnecessary at that point? it feels more natural to just let my body handle it once the symptoms are gone.",
